ViewObject.Name: TitleRecordView
ViewObject.SQLQuery:
SELECT TitleRecord.ID, TitleRecord.TITLE_ID, Title.CATALOG_NUMBER, Title.CATALOG_NUMBER AS CATALOG_NUMBER_1, TitleRecord.OVR_ID, TitleRecord.CONTENT_SOURCE, TitleRecord.PMID, TitleRecord.PM_TITLE, TitleRecord.SUB_TITLE, TitleRecord.SORT_TITLE, TitleRecord.EDITION, TitleRecord.QUALIFIER, TitleRecord.PART_NUMBER, TitleRecord.PART_NAME, Publisher.NAME, TitleRecord.PRIMARY_SOURCE_TYPE, TitleRecord.SECONDARY_SOURCE_TYPE, TitleRecord.SOURCE_TYPE, TitleRecord.BLOCK_BY_PUB_FLAG, TitleRecord.TRANSLATION_FLAG, TitleRecord.PUB_SEARCH_ALERT_FLAG, TitleRecord.VAULT_NAME, TitleRecord.PM_TYPE, TitleRecord.PM_GROUPS, TitleRecord.PM_FAMILY, TitleRecord.MANUFACTURING_PROCESS, TitleRecord.JOURNAL_CODE, (select count(ttrjc.JOURNAL_CODE) from trax_title_record ttrjc where ttrjc.JOURNAL_CODE = TitleRecord.JOURNAL_CODE) as JCodeCount, TitleRecord.IMAGE_STORAGE, TitleRecord.ASCII_STORAGE, TitleRecord.DOC_USAGE_ROYALTIES_FLAG, TitleRecord.COVER_IMAGE_TYPE, TitleRecord1.OVR_ID AltRightsOvrId, TitleRecord1.OVR_ID AltRightsOvrI2, nvl((select decode(count(ttrar.ALT_RIGHTS_TITLE_RECORD_ID), 0, 'N', 'Y') from trax_title_record ttrar where ttrar.ALT_RIGHTS_TITLE_RECORD_ID(+) = TitleRecord.ID), 'N') as AltRightsFlag, TitleRecord.CBL_ID, TitleRecord.COUNTRY_OF_PUBLICATION, TitleRecord.OK_FOR_EXPORT_FLAG, TitleRecord.GENERATION_METHOD, TitleRecord.CREATED_BY, TitleRecord.CREATED_DATE, trunc(TitleRecord.CREATED_DATE) as CREATED_BY_SEARCH, TitleRecord.LAST_UPDATED_BY, TitleRecord.LAST_UPDATED_DATE, trunc(TitleRecord.LAST_UPDATED_DATE) as LAST_UPDATE_BY_SEARCH, TitleRecord.LEGACY_PART_NUMBER, TitleRecord.ACRONYM, TitleRecord.PM_CLASS, TitleRecord.COVER_IMAGE_LOCATION_ID, Title.ID AS ID1, Title.CONTENT_OWNER_ID, Title.LONG_TITLE, Title.CATALOG_ROOT, Title.CATALOG_SUFFIX, Title.SHORT_TITLE, Publisher.ID AS ID2, TitleRecord1.ID ID3, TitleRecord.ALT_RIGHTS_TITLE_RECORD_ID, TitleRecord1.OVR_ID OvrId1, CoverImageTitleRecord.OVR_ID AS COVER_IMAGE_LOCATION, TitleRecord.AUTOGEN_RULE_SET,
TitleRecord.DO_NOT_USE, TitleRecord.content_model, TOCS.ID as ID4, TOCS.TITLE_RECORD_ID, TOCS.CONTENT_SOURCE_CUTOVER, trunc(TOCS.cs_cutover_created_date) as cs_cutover_created_date, TitleRecord.PUBLIC_ACCESS_CONTENT, TitleRecord.K12_SOURCE_TYPE, TitleRecord.UNSTRUCTURED_FLAG, TitleRecord.HIDE_FT_AVAILABILITY, TitleRecord.LINK_OUT_TYPE, TitleRecord.PUBLICATION_NOTE, TitleRecord.PUBLICATION_COVERAGE_NOTE FROM TRAX_TITLE_RECORD TitleRecord
INNER JOIN TRAX_TITLE Title ON TitleRecord.TITLE_ID = Title.ID
LEFT OUTER JOIN TRAX_OVR_PUBLISHER OvrPublisher INNER JOIN TRAX_PUBLISHER Publisher ON OvrPublisher.PUBLISHER_ID = Publisher.ID ON TitleRecord.ID = OvrPublisher.TITLE_RECORD_ID AND OvrPublisher.END_DATE is null
LEFT OUTER JOIN TRAX_TITLE_RECORD TitleRecord1 ON TitleRecord.ALT_RIGHTS_TITLE_RECORD_ID = TitleRecord1.ID
LEFT OUTER JOIN TRAX_TITLE_RECORD CoverImageTitleRecord ON TitleRecord.COVER_IMAGE_LOCATION_ID = CoverImageTitleRecord.ID
LEFT OUTER JOIN TRAX_OVR_CS_CUTOVER TOCS ON TitleRecord.ID = TOCS.TITLE_RECORD_ID
